#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.expm1.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.expm1"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:1 of
msgid "Calculate ``exp(x) - 1`` for all elements in the tensor."
msgstr "计算张量中所有元素的 ``exp(x) - 1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1 of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:3 of
msgid "Input values."
msgstr "输入值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）"
"的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1 of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:15 of
msgid "**out** -- Element-wise exponential minus one: ``out = exp(x) - 1``."
msgstr "**out** -- 元素级指数减一：``out = exp(x) - 1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1 of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`log1p`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:21 of
msgid "``log(1 + x)``, the inverse of expm1."
msgstr "``log(1 + x)``，expm1 的反函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:24 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:25 of
msgid ""
"This function provides greater precision than ``exp(x) - 1`` for small "
"values of ``x``."
msgstr "对于较小的 ``x`` 值，此函数比 ``exp(x) - 1`` 提供更高的精度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:29 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.expm1.expm1:30 of
msgid ""
"The true value of ``exp(1e-10) - 1`` is ``1.00000000005e-10`` to about 32"
" significant digits. This example shows the superiority of expm1 in this "
"case."
msgstr ""
"``exp(1e-10) - 1`` 的真实值约为 ``1.00000000005e-10``，精确到大约32位"
"有效数字。此示例展示了 expm1 在这种情况下更优的精度。"

